23:30.283 --> 23:31.743
[grunts] Idaho.

23:38.583 --> 23:41.378
[sirens blaring]

23:41.461 --> 23:42.754
Oh shit.

23:44.673 --> 23:45.966
[piano music playing]

23:46.049 --> 23:47.551
[indistinct chattering]

23:52.013 --> 23:53.056
[George sighs]

24:03.233 --> 24:04.234
[sighs]

24:13.368 --> 24:15.328
[woman] You aren't still sore, are you?

24:15.412 --> 24:18.832
